workflow.name: change_run_period_start_day_of_week
workflow.display_name: Change RunPeriod Start Day Of Week
workflow.measure_definition_display_name: Change RunPeriod Start Day Of Week
workflow.description: This is addressing issue with forward translation of OpenStudio Schedule Rulesets to Schedule Week in EnergyPlus. The start day of week for this logic appears to  apply that day of week to January 1st, however when the simulation is runEnergyPlus uses that as the day of the week for the RunPeriod, which for example may be July 25th, not January first. If I just change the start date.

Click the heading above a chart to view a table of the chart data.
